property ancestor, pSpr

on new me
  [  0] pushcons 0 .............................. <"objTransformer">
  [  2] pusharglist 1 ........................... <"objTransformer">
  [  4] extcall 27 .............................. <script("objTransformer")>
  [  6] pusharglist 1 ........................... <script("objTransformer")>
  [  8] extcall 0 ............................... <new(script("objTransformer"))>
  [ 10] setprop 77 .............................. ancestor = new(script("objTransformer"))
  [ 12] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 14] pushsymb 1 .............................. <#init>
  [ 16] pusharglist 2 ........................... <me, #init>
  [ 18] objcall 221 ............................. <me.modifyParams(#init)>
  [ 20] setlocal 0 .............................. i = me.modifyParams(#init)
  [ 22] getlocal 0 .............................. <i>
  [ 24] pushsymb 81 ............................. <#spr>
  [ 26] pushsymb 22 ............................. <#none>
  [ 28] pusharglistnoret 3 ...................... <i, #spr, #none>
  [ 30] objcall 37 .............................. i[#spr] = #none
  [ 32] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 34] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <me>
  [ 36] extcall 17 .............................. return me
  [ 38] ret
end

on init me, params
  [  0] getparam 1 .............................. <params>
  [  2] getobjprop 81 ........................... <params.spr>
  [  4] setprop 79 .............................. pSpr = params.spr
  [  6] getparam 1 .............................. <params>
  [  8] getprop 79 .............................. <pSpr>
