  [ 15] objcall 910 ............................. me.setCurrent(0)
  [ 18] pushzero ................................ <0>
  [ 19] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <0>
  [ 21] extcall 17 .............................. return 0
  [ 23] ret
end

on updateAttribute me
  [  0] getprop 79 .............................. <pSpr>
